dataIdInfo.idPurp: This dataset contains coldwater fishery classifications for all the major rivers in the Blackstone River watershed. This dataset was created for display purposes for the Blackstone River Coalition.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This vector dataset contains coldwater fishery classifications for the major rivers in the Blackstone River watershed. Fishery classifications were based on Rhode Island and Massachusetts assessment databases (RIGIS 2012, MassWildlife 2022). Rivers were derived from the National Hydrography Dataset (NHD 2023).
dataIdInfo.idCredit: RIGIS, MassWildlife, NHD, Narragansett Bay Estuary Program
